Operating system
================

Type name: os

Represents a specific version of an operating system.

Contains the information needed to install and configure an operating
system.


Files:

  os/<name>/pxelinux.yaml


YAML:

pxelinux.yaml:
  host:
    pxelinux:
      configfile: Path to PXELINUX configuration for installing this
                  OS by netboot, relative to the pxelinux.cfg directory
